# MDS Banner and Dashboard Typography Sizing

## Banner Typography

### Application Name
- **Size**: 1.5em
- Use for the application/product name in banner headers

```css
.banner__app-name {
  font-size: 1.5em;
}
```

## Dashboard Typography

### Page Title
- **Size**: 2em
- Use for the main dashboard page title
- **Alignment**: Depends on layout position (see alignment rules below)

```css
.dashboard__title {
  font-size: 2em;
}
```

### Subtitle
- **Size**: 1.2em
- Use for dashboard subtitles and section descriptions
- **Alignment**: Must match the title alignment

```css
.dashboard__subtitle {
  font-size: 1.2em;
}
```

### Title and Subtitle Alignment Rules

**If title is centered on the page:**
- Both title AND subtitle must be **center aligned**

**If title is placed on the left:**
- Both title AND subtitle must be **left aligned**

```css
/* Centered layout */
.dashboard__title-section--center {
  text-align: center;
}

.dashboard__title-section--center .dashboard__title,
.dashboard__title-section--center .dashboard__subtitle {
  text-align: center;
}

/* Left-aligned layout */
.dashboard__title-section--left {
  text-align: left;
}

.dashboard__title-section--left .dashboard__title,
.dashboard__title-section--left .dashboard__subtitle {
  text-align: left;
}
```

### Full-Screen Width Widget Title
- **Size**: 1.4em
- Use for titles of widgets that span the full width of the screen

```css
.dashboard-widget--full-width .widget__title {
  font-size: 1.4em;
}
```

## Examples

### ✅ GOOD - Banner with Application Name

```tsx
<header className="banner">
  <h1 style={{ fontSize: '1.5em' }}>MyApp Dashboard</h1>
</header>
```

### ✅ GOOD - Dashboard with Centered Title and Subtitle

```tsx
<div className="dashboard">
  <div className="dashboard__title-section" style={{ textAlign: 'center' }}>
    <h1 style={{ fontSize: '2em', textAlign: 'center' }}>Analytics Overview</h1>
    <p style={{ fontSize: '1.2em', textAlign: 'center' }}>Key metrics and insights</p>
  </div>
  
  <div className="widget widget--full-width">
    <h2 style={{ fontSize: '1.4em' }}>Revenue Trends</h2>
  </div>
</div>
```

### ✅ GOOD - Dashboard with Left-Aligned Title and Subtitle

```tsx
<div className="dashboard">
  <div className="dashboard__title-section" style={{ textAlign: 'left' }}>
    <h1 style={{ fontSize: '2em', textAlign: 'left' }}>Analytics Overview</h1>
    <p style={{ fontSize: '1.2em', textAlign: 'left' }}>Key metrics and insights</p>
  </div>
  
  <div className="widget widget--full-width">
    <h2 style={{ fontSize: '1.4em' }}>Revenue Trends</h2>
  </div>
</div>
```

### ❌ BAD - Inconsistent Sizing

```tsx
<div className="dashboard">
  <h1 style={{ fontSize: '1.8em' }}>Analytics</h1> {/* Should be 2em */}
  <p style={{ fontSize: '1em' }}>Metrics</p> {/* Should be 1.2em */}
</div>
```

### ❌ BAD - Mismatched Alignment

```tsx
<div className="dashboard">
  <h1 style={{ fontSize: '2em', textAlign: 'center' }}>Analytics Overview</h1>
  <p style={{ fontSize: '1.2em', textAlign: 'left' }}>Key metrics</p> {/* Should be center aligned */}
</div>
```
